==English==
===Noun===
'''racketeer'''

# one who commits crimes (especially [[fraud]], [[bribery]], [[loanshark|loansharking]], [[extortion]] etc.) to aid in running a shady or [[illegal]] business.
# one who [[instigate|instigates]] or has [[involvement]] with a [[racket]].

===Verb===
'''racketeer, racketeering'''

# the act of commiting [[illegal]] business activities or criminal [[schemes]].
# crime [[systematically]] carried out by a criminal [[organizations]].